{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0003", "text": "爲何你那牀頭玩具熊 再找不到", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 5, 5, 0, 0, 9, 2, 0, 4, 9, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ho4", "nei5", "naa5", "cong4", "tau4", "waan2", "geoi6", "hung4", "zoi3", "zaau2", "bat1", "dou3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "爲何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "牀頭", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "玩具", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "熊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "找", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不到", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "防不勝防", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_236", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0004", "text": "花樽的花 偏偏天天轉色", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 3, 3, 3, 3, 3, 3, 9, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["faa1", "zeon1", "dik1", "faa1", "pin1", "pin1", "tin1", "tin1", "zyun2", "sik1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "花", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "樽", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "花", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "偏偏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天天", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "轉色", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "防不勝防", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_236", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0005", "text": "也許這刻你 仍然尚未發覺", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 9, 5, 3, 5, 0, 0, 2, 2, 4, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jaa5", "heoi2", "ze5", "hak1", "nei5", "jing4", "jin4", "soeng6", "mei6", "faat3", "gok3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "也許", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這刻", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "仍然", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "尚未", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "發覺", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "防不勝防", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_236", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0006", "text": "家中有這一個訪客 時時漏夜冒昧探你", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 5, 5, 3, 4, 9, 4, 0, 0, 2, 2, 2, 2, 4, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["gaa1", "zung1", "jau5", "ze5", "jat1", "go3", "fong2", "haak3", "si4", "si4", "lau6", "je6", "mou6", "mui6", "taam3", "nei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "家中", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "訪客", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "時時", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "漏夜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "冒昧", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "探", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "防不勝防", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_236", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0007", "text": "將瑣碎東西帶走 然後又放低", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 9, 4, 3, 3, 4, 9, 0, 2, 2, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zoeng1", "so2", "seoi3", "dung1", "sai1", "daai3", "zau2", "jin4", "hau6", "jau6", "fong3", "dai1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "將", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "瑣碎", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "東西", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "帶走", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "然後", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "又", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "放低", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "防不勝防", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_236", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0008", "text": "在你的唱機放低唱片是我", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 3, 4, 3, 4, 3, 4, 9, 2, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zoi6", "nei5", "dik1", "coeng3", "gei1", "fong3", "dai1", "coeng3", "pin2", "si6", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "唱機", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "放", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "低", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "唱片", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "防不勝防", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_236", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjM2_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
